Defendant Khristiana L Palmer not in court with attorney Nicole Williams Buttery for Tedia K. Gamino.  Michael Thurston appeared for the State of Wisconsin. Defendant did not appear, case was set for 10:30 a.m., case was called at 10:47 a.m.  Based on defendant's non appearance, Court orders bail be revoked and forfieted.  Court issues capias.
